This repository contains exercise files, Codespace configuration, Model Context
Protocol (MCP) server bundles, skills, prompts, and supporting materials
(the "Materials") provided by Learn Data Insights ("LDI") as companion content
for the LinkedIn Learning course "Data & AI Strategy with Microsoft Fabric"
(the "Course").

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
