LDI grants you a personal, non-exclusive, non-transferable, non-sublicensable,
revocable licence to access, download, run, and modify the Materials solely
for the purpose of:

  (a) learning from and completing the exercises in the Course;
  (b) experimenting with the Materials against the sample datasets bundled
      with this repository (e.g. the Landon Hotels fictional data); and
  (c) experimenting with the Materials against your own synthetic,
      non-production, non-confidential data for personal learning purposes.

No other rights are granted. All rights not expressly granted are reserved.

