5. DATA HANDLING AND PRIVACY
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

The MCP servers in this Codespace process data that you place into the
workspace or submit via GitHub Copilot Chat. That data is transmitted to the
MCP server processes and to GitHub Copilot for language model inference, and
may be logged, stored, or processed by those services in accordance with their
own terms.

You are solely responsible for what data you place into this environment.
Do NOT upload, paste, or otherwise submit into this Codespace any data that
is confidential, personally identifiable, regulated (including under GDPR,
HIPAA, PCI-DSS, or similar), covered by a non-disclosure agreement, or
otherwise not cleared for transmission to third-party cloud services.

